#

Easy Beet Borscht with Canned Beets

30 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasyQuick

Description

A vibrant and hearty soup, perfect for a cozy meal, made easy with canned beets!

Ingredients

  • canned beets: 2 cans
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
